column1: Components of 5- and 10-year nominal yields and inflation compensation and 5-to-10-year nominal forward rate and forward inflation compensation.
D'Amico, Kim, and Wei (2018), "Tips from TIPS: The Informational Content of Treasury Inflation-Protected Security Prices,"
updated by Kim, Walsh, and Wei (2019), FEDS notes, "Tips from TIPS: Update and Discussions."
Data are updated monthly; all rates are in percentage points.

This release is based on a model re-estimation using data through November 12, 2025.  Other changes relative to the Kim, Walsh, and Wei (2019) FEDS note include using 1-year survey inflation forecasts from Blue Chip Financial Forecasts (monthly) instead of 1-year survey inflation forecasts from Survey of Professional Forecasters (quarterly) and adding 15- and 20-year nominal and TIPS yields to the estimation.

This is not an official Federal Reserve statistical release. Because this is a staff research product and not an official statistical release, it is subject to delay, revision, or methodological changes without advance notice.
